 224:Core/Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Include/cmsis_gcc.h **** /**
 225:Core/Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Include/cmsis_gcc.h ****   \brief   No Operation
 226:Core/Src/Drivers/CMSIS/Include/cmsis_gcc.h ****   \details No Operation does nothing. This instruction can be used for code alignment purposes.
